description: As a Marine fighter pilot, Amy McGrath broke many barriers for women in the military. Her experience has already carried her to an upset victory in the Democratic primary for a House seat in Kentucky. Here’s how her campaign hopes to win in November.
title: Can Amy McGrath’s Military Experience Carry Her to Victory in Kentucky?
title_page: Can Amy McGrath’s Military Experience Carry Her to Victory in Kentucky? - Video - NYTimes.com
